Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.53,0:00:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi Hideyoshi, the world's foremost busting out machine. From Chiba Prefecture. {from OG subs, no clue what to make of 天下一のぶっ飛びマシーン }
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.01,0:00:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oda Shintaro. A one-hit wonder who is ignorant of theory. From Chiba Prefecture.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.51,0:00:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokugawa Yasube. An absolute ignoramus who doesn't know when to stop calling. From Chiba. {https://www.weblio.jp/content/%E3%82%BF%E3%82%B3%E9%B3%B4%E3%81%8D - something about calling carelessly ; /with zero knowledge on theory}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.02,0:00:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Akechi Koichi. The expert in by-the-book calculative and rational playstyle. From Chiba.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.52,0:00:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayami Akina. \NTechnically Toyotomi's love interest.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.57,0:00:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Born with incredible luck. \NFrom Chiba Prefecture.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.47,0:00:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.83,0:00:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.93,0:01:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.79,0:01:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Zu... ga... n.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.99,0:01:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost against those three at mahjong again, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.28,0:01:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugan.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.32,0:01:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made a mistake.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.49,0:01:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Luckless.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.32,0:01:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to quit mahjong, but in the end, \Nthat'd just mean running away from the problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.23,0:01:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you give up on a sour note, you’ll carry the label of a loser for the rest of your days!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.17,0:01:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Luckless?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.37,0:01:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So you’ve gotta hit back at them with everything you’ve got, like a real man!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.72,0:01:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.13,0:01:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are those the famous...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.81,0:01:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Luckless flowers?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.63,0:01:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Luckless...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.15,0:01:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi-kun, come with me for a second.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.66,0:02:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.63,0:02:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My friend Ide-san is a mahjong pro, \Nand this is his dojo! {井出}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.41,0:02:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hayami-kun! \NLong time no see.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.77,0:02:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this Toyotomi-kun who needs the special training
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.42,0:02:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,from me, the University of Tokyo graduate?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.15,0:02:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Please be nice to him!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.79,0:02:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No, wait. Uh...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.42,0:02:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,As the University of Tokyo graduate, I’ll do everything in my power
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.86,0:02:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to turn Toyotomi-kun into the strongest, unbeatable mahjong player.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.33,0:02:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I don't wanna! Akina-chan! What the...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.96,0:02:36.42,Thought,,0,0,0,,Do your best, Toyotomi!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.39,0:02:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this room?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.28,0:02:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not mentioned it before, but actually, I've graduated from the University of Tokyo.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.78,0:02:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that three times already!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.23,0:02:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,As a University of Tokyo programming graduate,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.63,0:02:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll now teach you the basics of computer mahjong.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.22,0:02:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously? Isn't it just a mahjong video game?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.09,0:03:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, until now, there's been heaps of so-called "mahjong video games."
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.94,0:03:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,However, none of them are able to recreate mahjong's artistic and theoretical qualities.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.09,0:03:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because they're made by a bunch of poorly educated country bumpkins
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.36,0:03:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,who just popped out of school!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.05,0:03:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I like strip mahjong though...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.55,0:03:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! That's why you're so bad at mahjong!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.61,0:03:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And I, a University of Tokyo graduate, am always right!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.87,0:03:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I'll play it!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.53,0:03:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Like he said, \Nit seems pretty serious.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.19,0:03:45.75,Thought,,0,0,0,,All right, let's win this! The dealer is my toimen, Ide-pro, huh...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.62,0:03:49.21,Thought,,0,0,0,,I have two dora.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.35,0:03:52.35,Thought,,0,0,0,,That's a decent hand!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.09,0:03:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.70,0:03:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenhou ryuuiisou!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.13,0:04:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugaaan...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.10,0:04:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this game?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.06,0:04:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,As a University of Tokyo graduate, I must always be perfect, even within the computer!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.06,0:04:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite a shitty game though! {kusoge}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.98,0:04:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenhou chuuren poutou!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.44,0:04:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugaaan!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.83,0:04:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi ippatsu tsumo daisangen!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.11,0:04:42.40,Thought,,0,0,0,,Dammit... He's done it 2627 times straight since last night...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.40,0:04:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Let's move on to the second stage of training!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.33,0:04:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.16,0:04:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it this time?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.35,0:04:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is psyche strengthening machine, invented by me, the University of Tokyo graduate!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.11,0:05:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Psyche strengthening machine?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.03,0:05:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This'll let you experience \Nthe virtual reality mahjong.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.12,0:05:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to keep watching these images without blinking.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.99,0:05:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You left me no choice! {/I couldn't [blink] even if I wanted to}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.12,0:05:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As you watch, your psychic state \Nwill be displayed here as a waveform.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.15,0:05:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us begin, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.78,0:05:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron! Mentanpin sanshoku iipeikou!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.72,0:05:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugan!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.02,0:05:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're sitting on is an electric chair, through which a million volts of electric current
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.50,0:05:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,will flow whenever your mental state becomes disturbed.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.81,0:05:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How much?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.99,0:05:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,To avoid getting fried, keep your psychic waves under control.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.53,0:05:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a strong psyche, \Nthere is no victory in mahjong!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.50,0:05:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass! Pass! Pass!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.27,0:05:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ippatsu tsumo!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.53,0:05:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakuman!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.25,0:06:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugaaaaan!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.72,0:06:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{missing in OG subs, muzu's time to shine}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.68,0:06:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.56,0:06:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.97,0:06:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.95,0:06:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.00,0:06:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.78,0:06:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.20,0:06:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.45,0:06:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.44,0:06:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, it's a success.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.54,0:06:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.60,0:06:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it, Toyotomi-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.43,0:06:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You did really well enduring all that at Ide-san's place for a whole month!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.58,0:07:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.44,0:07:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.40,0:07:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use talking to him now.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.71,0:07:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside his mind, all that matters is winning at mahjong, and he won't respond to anything else.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.51,0:07:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.33,0:07:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a machine.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.81,0:07:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Setting aside trivial emotions, he can steadily advance his hand with composure and logic.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.30,0:07:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He has been reborn as a mahjong-playing machine.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.95,0:07:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask you \Nto change his personality!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.82,0:07:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all for the victory.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.43,0:07:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who has made the greatest sacrifices will ultimately emerge as the winner!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.08,0:07:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unreasonable...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.67,0:07:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from the University of Tokyo!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.29,0:08:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's roll.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.58,0:08:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That's some nerve you got to challenge us.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.53,0:08:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, the look in his eyes is different from usual.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Didja catch conjunctivitis or something? {けつまく えんで ねーか?}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.49,0:08:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! They're starting!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.22,0:08:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from the University of Tokyo.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.85,0:08:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How is he sorting his tiles so fast?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.60,0:08:44.95,Thought,,0,0,0,,This hand...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.22,0:08:52.74,Thought,,0,0,0,,To aim thoroughly for 567 sanshoku, discard 4s.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.74,0:08:57.53,Thought,,0,0,0,,However, the disadvantage of ending up with a bad wait is too big.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.53,0:09:02.41,Thought,,0,0,0,,Discard 5m to lock in 678. This is the widest hand.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.41,0:09:08.42,Thought,,0,0,0,,Even if I draw 5p, I can discard 5s and expect mangan with riichi on the dora suji.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.42,0:09:14.41,Thought,,0,0,0,,Finally, there is discarding 5s, but this makes the hand extremely narrow if I draw 58p or 36s.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.41,0:09:18.64,Thought,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, it leaves both kinds of sanshoku feasible.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.64,0:09:25.15,Thought,,0,0,0,,However, if I draw 8s and try to go for 678 sanshoku, it's one move slower.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.15,0:09:29.63,Thought,,0,0,0,,That being said, here discarding from the 5s anko early is the optimal move.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.92,0:09:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? He discarded 5s?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.08,0:09:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax. He's a machine.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.11,0:09:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Between drawing a tile and discarding, he calculates through a million possibilities
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.20,0:09:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,in just 0.5 seconds.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.18,0:09:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And then he makes the best possible move.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.13,0:09:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.82,0:09:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.07,0:09:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanshoku doukou sanankou tanyao dora 3!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.76,0:09:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Baiman!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.00,0:10:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugaan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.46,0:10:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He dealt in? {believing the OG subs but not sure}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.97,0:10:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How was that the best possible move?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.60,0:10:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This outcome was precalculated too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.56,0:10:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at him closely!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.11,0:10:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. Even the way he says "Zugan" \Ndoesn't break his composure.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.68,0:10:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron! Junchan sanshoku pinfu iipeikou!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.62,0:10:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.15,0:10:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky! Pinfu ryanpeikou dora dora!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.41,0:10:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.51,0:10:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.04,0:10:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's riichi ippatsu chinitsu ittsuu dora 1!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.98,0:10:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.90,0:10:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a machine!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.05,0:10:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.18,0:11:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The precision to deal in the takame every time!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.61,0:11:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The increased durability to keep dealing in without flinching!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.23,0:11:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you saying...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.12,0:11:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he has become...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.90,0:11:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Without exaggerating, the world's strongest...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.53,0:11:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dealing-in machine!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.84,0:11:22.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thus, Toyotomi was remodeled
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.29,0:11:26.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,by the University of Tokyo mahjong pundit Ide \Ninto a perfect dealing-in machine.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.60,0:11:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.75,0:11:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisangen.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.68,0:11:35.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will the day ever come when he can return to the ways of the world? Stay strong, Toyotomi!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.84,0:11:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.31,0:12:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The first prize ski trip! \NThe first prize ski trip!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.28,0:12:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.01,0:12:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, too bad! You win tissue paper. \NTough luck!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.75,0:12:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugan!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.89,0:12:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine! All last!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.75,0:12:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,yakuman!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.50,0:12:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.79,0:12:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.15,0:12:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Akina-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.51,0:12:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.90,0:12:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Congratulations!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.35,0:12:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! I did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.82,0:12:27.31,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Great! That's our Akina-chan! You're amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.82,0:12:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Toyotomi-kun! Let's slide!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.04,0:12:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.98,0:12:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.01,0:12:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi-kun! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.41,0:12:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Will be there now! Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.22,0:12:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.42,0:12:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's just like you, Toyotomi-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.82,0:13:03.80,Thought,,0,0,0,,Akina-chan is so cute!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.80,0:13:08.43,Thought,,0,0,0,,But, when two go skiing together, \Nthe après-ski is a matter of course! {after-ski is more clear and that's what we hear but this one is a more common}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.95,0:13:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going first, Toyotomi-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.38,0:13:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just the two of us, Toyotomi-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.46,0:13:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the two of us, Akina-chan...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.32,0:13:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling a bit tipsy...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.49,0:13:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go to bed, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.31,0:13:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Akina-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.92,0:13:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, aren't you rushing things, Toyotomi-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.44,0:13:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Akina-chan...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.75,0:13:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whassat?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.10,0:13:37.90,Overlap,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.50,0:13:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.71,0:13:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,T-These voices!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.47,0:13:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Move it, move it, move it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.93,0:13:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What the... What the... What the... What the...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.37,0:13:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I really just see...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.26,0:13:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo! If it isn't Toyotomi!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.29,0:13:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What a coincidence!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.78,0:14:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, what are the odds?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.43,0:14:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,To think we'd end up in neighboring rooms at the same inn!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.61,0:14:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you three just follow me here?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.43,0:14:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you on about? We won the ski trip from that same lottery.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.65,0:14:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes sense that we stayed\N in the same inn! {pension }
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.26,0:14:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! These guys too?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.22,0:14:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This will make our après-ski \Na lot more exciting!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.24,0:14:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's get straight to it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.19,0:14:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do something, Akina-chan... {no clue, naze ya?}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.33,0:14:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't act like a spoiled kid!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.91,0:14:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn right, men belong in the men's world!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.00,0:14:38.58,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Akina-chan...!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.27,0:14:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.03,0:14:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a pon!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.78,0:14:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna pon that chun too.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.04,0:14:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.25,0:14:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why stop now?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.25,0:14:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,4m!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.21,0:15:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Impressive!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.73,0:15:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I call ultra-cool mahjong!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.19,0:15:08.09,Thought,,0,0,0,,I got to tenpai but I can't discard 4s...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.09,0:15:12.38,Thought,,0,0,0,,It's time for the trustworthy technique: genbutsu of two players!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.06,0:15:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Weak.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.31,0:15:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Passing the bump that is Yasu
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.71,0:15:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and dodging Shintaro's frozen tree, \Nmagnificent mawashi-uchi! {信太郎の樹氷をかわす華麗な回し打ち!}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.58,0:15:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My parallel technique!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.02,0:15:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron! Tanyao sanshoku dora 1!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.49,0:15:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugaaan!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.45,0:15:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.04,0:15:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugan. Zugan. Zugan. \NZugan, Zugan, Zugan!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.49,0:15:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugaaan...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.72,0:15:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, Toyotomi? \NLast place again?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.77,0:15:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's switch, Toyotomi-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me play instead of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.75,0:15:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're hopeless, Akina-chan...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.67,0:15:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No more hopeless than you!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.42,0:15:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you say so...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.98,0:15:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please do! Play with me! Let's play together! \NWe'll keep playing all night! {probably with some lewd insinuations - 打つべ\N打つべ\Nオラと麻雀\N打つベーど}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.32,0:15:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasu, you're drooling.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.58,0:16:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? That's a pretty good haipai.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.82,0:16:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You start discarding with the honors, like this, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.67,0:16:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh! Oh no, I dropped my pair of pei!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.72,0:16:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.55,0:16:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? It's another pei!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.56,0:16:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That's a win for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.93,0:16:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! I would have won from the start and you didn't tell me, Toyotomi!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.05,0:16:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, you sure are lucky... \NTsumo dora 1 is 1000 all, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.76,0:16:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, thanks! \NLook at this, Toyotomi-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.91,0:16:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? He fell over...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.79,0:16:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because he's a snowflake.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.69,0:16:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, then. I can do it by myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.65,0:16:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.88,0:16:51.11,Thought,,0,0,0,,Her luck just doesn't end...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.33,0:16:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Ippatsu tsumo!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.29,0:16:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.29,0:16:57.50,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Huh-uh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.50,0:17:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I had it... \NBut not this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.46,0:17:05.30,Thought,,0,0,0,,Jeez... How long are we gonna let her keep stringing us along? {unsure}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.26,0:17:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, my bad! \NThe tiles stuck together, ya know!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.94,0:17:15.03,Thought,,0,0,0,,So, pinfu ryanpeikou dora dora, or, chiitoitsu dora dora...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.03,0:17:17.68,Thought,,0,0,0,,Which one should I go for, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.32,0:17:20.94,Thought,,0,0,0,,4p was the girl's tsumo!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.37,0:17:24.17,Thought,,0,0,0,,Riichi with this one!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.61,0:17:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.42,0:17:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Haneman!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.83,0:17:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.70,0:17:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I got tsumo!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.03,0:17:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.42,0:17:35.86,Thought,,0,0,0,,The hell? 47p shanpon? Unthinkable! {no clue what's last word}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.86,0:17:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What a stupid wait... {タコ待ちだ}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.79,0:17:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh, with riichi and tsumo, \Nit's toitoi, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.75,0:17:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi tsumo...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.23,0:17:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Toitoi?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.22,0:17:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man, would you look at the time!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.67,0:17:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, gotta go to sleep soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.70,0:17:59.09,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Right, right, it's bad for my skin. {was "まいったまいった明日にひびくぜ" in manga but ohada definitely doesn't sound like ashita}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.09,0:18:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.64,0:18:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha... Didn't you faint earlier?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.16,0:18:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! I saw it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.60,0:18:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Faint? Why would I?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.91,0:18:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna go back to your room, \Npay up that 16,000 all first!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.17,0:18:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Akina-chan! \NYou just made up for all my losses!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.60,0:18:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Akina! Akina!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.56,0:18:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was just getting in the mood...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.95,0:18:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Double ton dora 3, ni-
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.93,0:18:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.78,0:18:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.86,0:18:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? This is a top hand!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.16,0:18:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! My kanchan!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.82,0:18:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi ippatsu double ton dora 3!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.40,0:18:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,With ura being 6m, that's dealer's baiman!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.24,0:18:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that rocks, all right... {no clue, not in manga}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.38,0:18:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.09,0:18:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.59,0:18:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.09,0:18:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.55,0:18:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron! Tsumo!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.45,0:18:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.99,0:18:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.59,0:19:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.58,0:19:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.54,0:19:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That woman is no joke...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.76,0:19:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly she's at the top with 300,000. {いきなり30万点のトップだかんな}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.50,0:19:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, isn't that amazing, Akina-chan! \NTwo people dealt in and you got a yakuman!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.21,0:19:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi-kun, I'm sleepy. \NCan I go to bed?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.17,0:19:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure! \NI'll handle it from here.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.40,0:19:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you should be okay with 300,000 of advantage, Toyotomi-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.59,0:19:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.21,0:19:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.99,0:19:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can lose to these dolts now! \NEasy win, easy money!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.03,0:19:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.26,0:19:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy win... against us?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.07,0:19:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'm gonna lose to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.79,0:19:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all so intimidating!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.00,0:19:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But a 300,000 point lead \Nis not that easy to close!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.63,0:19:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron! Mentanpin sanshoku!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.65,0:19:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just 8,000 for now, \N300,000 is still a way off...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.09,0:20:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It is a way off, as you say. \NThe first place is clearly mine already.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.63,0:20:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Why don't you just accept it already and go for second?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.06,0:20:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.06,0:20:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron! Menhon double ton! \NDamn it, that's not even haneman...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.35,0:20:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I really needed a dora...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.13,0:20:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Even 12,000 is still not a big deal...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.75,0:20:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No... It isn't!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.70,0:20:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron! Chiitoi dora dora!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.66,0:20:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Double ron! Ittsuu dora dora!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.63,0:20:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, it's this late already?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.03,0:20:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya tomorrow! \NI gotta sleep too.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.33,0:20:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.10,0:20:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No quitting without a rematch! {/when you're ahead isn't allowed!}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.91,0:20:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna go to sleep, you're gonna have to play with us for at least 10 hanchans more!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.42,0:20:42.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And so, Toyotomi's hellish après-ski night dragged on.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.06,0:20:47.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ah! That sweet dream of spending the night with Akina, whither is it now?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.62,0:20:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Toyotomi-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.61,0:20:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.66,0:20:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugaaan...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.65,0:20:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,T-There's no way...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.87,0:21:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid Toyotomi-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.28,0:21:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Super Zugan!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.00,0:21:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I'm way luckier than Toyotomi-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.25,0:21:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I should also try to play mahjong more often now?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.09,0:21:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh no, I have to move! {no clue what she means, will try to remember to check again after the next episode}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.99,0:21:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Super Zugan:
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.11,0:21:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rake Zugan \Nand Akina Once More. {カッパギヅガン / 明菜ふたたび}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.36,0:21:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely watch it!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.81,0:21:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you fall asleep!
